Description: Mengklik \"Daftar Sekarang\" untuk masuk ke halaman Home/Beranda
Menunggu hingga button sebelum Humburger button di klik
Mengklik Hamburger Button kemdian memilih Operasional untuk masuk ke halaman Kasir, Stock, Pengeluaran dan Rincian
Mengklik \"Operasional\" untuk bisa direct ke screen Stock
Remove product from Shopping Cart by Tapping - button
Remove product from Shopping Cart - by Typing
Increase product amount in Shopping Cart - by Tapping + button
Increase product amount in Shopping Cart - by Typing
Increase product amount in Shopping Cart - while selected product = stock
Increase product amount in Shopping Cart - until Products stock less than 10
Decrease product amount in Shopping Cart by Tapping - button
Decrease product amount in Shopping Cart - by Typing
Decrease product amount in Shopping Cart - until Products stock more than 10
